Jenny's last surgery.

284
00:13:06,035 --> 00:13:08,152
I just had a feeling.

285
00:13:08,221 --> 00:13:10,855
I said goodbye. I left for work.

286
00:13:10,923 --> 00:13:12,139
I was two blocks away

287
00:13:12,208 --> 00:13:15,643
and I had an awful,
just sick feeling.

288
00:13:15,712 --> 00:13:18,012
I turned around, I drove
home, and there she was.

289
00:13:18,081 --> 00:13:21,065
On the floor, blood everywhere.

290
00:13:21,133 --> 00:13:22,812
I just had a terrible feeling

291
00:13:22,836 --> 00:13:25,320
that something was really wrong.

292
00:13:26,572 --> 00:13:28,692
It's a good thing you did.

293
00:13:36,016 --> 00:13:39,117
