to stick around for me.

436
00:19:36,192 --> 00:19:38,258
It was a horrible mistake.

437
00:19:38,327 --> 00:19:40,811
The custody battle? Me
breaking up with Kyle.

438
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:42,780
I told you that. Who's Kyle?

439
00:19:42,849 --> 00:19:44,531
He was a
once-in-a-lifetime butt.

440
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:45,800
