00:21:42,652 --> 00:21:45,052
I love you.

492
00:21:45,855 --> 00:21:47,354
Okay. No, no, no.

493
00:21:47,423 --> 00:21:49,367
No, I don't want to
talk to Mommy, okay?

494
00:21:49,391 --> 00:21:50,791
Okay, bye...

