538
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:19,818
That's okay. We will
make waffles, or...

539
00:24:19,842 --> 00:24:21,308
I'm going with you.

540
00:24:21,377 --> 00:24:24,111
I can't. Oh, I can't.
Mommy can't today.

541
00:24:24,179 --> 00:24:25,674
I'm running late, and
you're here to play with Zola,

542
00:24:25,698 --> 00:24:27,109
but I will be back
just as soon as I can.

543
00:24:27,133 --> 00:24:28,593
No.

544
00:24:28,617 --> 00:24:29,816
I'm sorry.

545
00:24:29,885 --> 00:24:31,401
I'm sorry. I love you.

546
00:24:31,471 --> 00:24:32,514
I hate you.

547
00:24:32,538 --> 00:24:34,565
Okay, let's go find Zola.

548
00:24:34,589 --> 00:24:35,934
