558
00:24:52,674 --> 00:24:54,252
Shut up. She's got
enough on her plate today.

559
00:24:54,276 --> 00:24:55,954
Okay, look. If Russo
says watch and wait,

560
00:24:55,978 --> 00:24:57,277
I say we watch and wait.

561
00:24:57,346 --> 00:24:59,057
Any evidence of fetal
distress on the monitor,

562
00:24:59,081 --> 00:25:00,530
