563
00:25:02,601 --> 00:25:05,819
And Dr. Torres and Sofia
couldn't possibly be any closer.

564
00:25:05,888 --> 00:25:08,033
So, you've seen them together
frequently over the years.

565
00:25:08,057 --> 00:25:10,273
All the time. They went
to the same daycare

566
00:25:10,343 --> 00:25:11,909
