00:28:26,972 --> 00:28:28,884
They kept a running tally.

646
00:28:28,908 --> 00:28:32,042
Does this piece of
evidence, Document 3C,

647
00:28:33,545 --> 00:28:35,028
refresh your recollection?

648
00:28:38,300 --> 00:28:40,884
You've won 25 times
in the past six months.

649
00:28:40,953 --> 00:28:43,664
That's 25 nights Dr. Robbins
was out drinking with you,

650
00:28:43,688 --> 00:28:45,989
not including the
times you lost.

651
00:28:48,127 --> 00:28:49,470
Where was Sofia
during those evenings?

652
00:28:49,494 --> 00:28:50,927
I don't know.

653
00:28:50,980 --> 00:28:52,440
I'm sorry. I didn't... I
didn't quite catch that.

654
00:28:52,464 --> 00:28:55,248
I said I wasn't privy to
her childcare schedule.

655
00:28:55,317 --> 00:28:57,850
I would like to introduce
into evidence Document 4C.

656
00:28:57,919 --> 00:28:59,870
