showing decreased variability.

729
00:32:56,057 --> 00:32:57,657
Well, what can we do?

730
00:32:57,725 --> 00:32:59,553
I can deliver, then you do
what you can for the baby.

731
00:32:59,577 --> 00:33:01,956
Look, it's hard to keep those
babies alive. The odds suck.

732
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:04,130
Compromised lungs,
high risk of brain bleeds.

733
00:33:04,199 --> 00:33:06,328
It's the only option left.

734
00:33:06,352 --> 00:33:07,950
It's what we're doing.

735
00:33:09,971 --> 00:33:11,521
So, I just lied to my daughter,

736
00:33:11,589 --> 00:33:13,039
and I will go back in there

737
00:33:13,108 --> 00:33:15,541
and keep telling her that
she'll be okay no matter what,

738
00:33:15,611 --> 00:33:17,589
but to do that, I need to
know that you have done

739
00:33:17,613 --> 00:33:20,096
everything in your
power to make this okay.

740
00:33:20,165 --> 00:33:21,414
Can you tell me that?

741
00:33:21,483 --> 00:33:23,550
Tell me that you have
done everything you can

742
00:33:23,619 --> 00:33:26,185
to keep my baby
and grandchild alive.

743
00:33:30,843 --> 00:33:32,776
Robbins wouldn't deliver.

744
00:33:32,845 --> 00:33:34,925
Do you have another option?

745
00:33:37,599 --> 00:33:39,359
Then I'll see you in surgery.

746
00:33:40,668 --> 00:33:42,269
Is Robbins an option?

747
00:33:42,604 --> 00:33:43,870
No.

748
00:33:52,714 --> 00:33:55,248
Dr. Robbins, you
were with Dr. Torres

749
00:33:55,317 --> 00:33:56,766
before she was pregnant. Yes.

750
00:33:56,834 --> 00:33:57,834
Were you together

751
00:33:57,903 --> 00:33:58,980
when she got pregnant? No.

